'''Liberation Lake''' was a [[lake]] in [[Unity Green]] on the planet [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]], five years after the end of the [[Yuuzhan Vong]] war. Its rolling whitecaps were home to [[yammal-jell]]s and [[coufee]] eels; favored prey of the native [[Hawk-bat/Legends|hawk-bat]]. The lake also contained [[y'luubi]], which [[Mara Jade Skywalker]] enjoyed at a dinner meeting held by [[Aryn Dro Thul|Aryn Thul]] at [[Yuza Bre]] in [[36 ABY]]. On one of its shores, [[yorik coral]] bluffs marked the edge of the park.

